SELECT ul.user_id, ul.action_type, ul.time_stamp, ud.device_name, ul.IP_address FROM UserLogs ul JOIN UserDevices ud ON ul.user_id = ud.user_id WHERE ul.action_type = 'Logout' AND ud.device_type = 'Desktop' ORDER BY ul.time_stamp DESC LIMIT 5;
